{"tid":1659990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國化工廠突爆炸屋頂飛脫 至少4死6傷","createTime":"2019-10-17T08:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T08:54:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a1479ff3975b2bfd3b6b0786a5e3c28fc39bd63","tid":1659990,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpM21k6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpM21k6q.jpg&h=86bfc741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國再度傳出工廠爆炸意外！在廣西陸川縣一處工業區，在今中午突然爆炸，造成至少4死6傷，目前正搶救中。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中國媒體報導，廣西玉林一家化工廠今（15日）中午11點15分左右，突然發生爆炸，工廠屋頂直接被炸飛，邊牆也嚴重毀壞，現場冒出粉紅色濃煙，散發濃濃異味，目前已知至少4死2重傷4輕傷，相關單位已經到場，做緊急處置。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2946791\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2946791&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=1a05b3db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2946791&h=e50d8dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2946791</a>"},{"pid":"a353529a5ee05cc1836a568579f8e6dc7d46a356","tid":1659990,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}